articles.title: Julian Assange returns home as free man to Australia, after plea deal with US - CNN
articles.description: WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange has landed back home in Australia, a free man for the first time in 12 years, after a US judge signed off on his unexpected plea deal on Wednesday morning.
